WEBVTT

00:12:30.080 --> 00:12:32.920
So when men share housework and childcare,

00:12:33.920 --> 00:12:36.696
their children are happier and healthier,

00:12:36.720 --> 00:12:38.400
and men want this.

00:12:39.520 --> 00:12:41.936
When men share housework and childcare,

00:12:41.960 --> 00:12:44.600
their wives are happier. Duh.

00:12:45.720 --> 00:12:48.176
Not only that, their wives are healthier.

00:12:48.200 --> 00:12:50.391
Their wives are less likely
to see a therapist,

00:12:50.415 --> 00:12:52.463
less likely to be diagnosed
with depression,

00:12:52.487 --> 00:12:56.256
less likely to be put on medication,
more likely to go to the gym,

00:12:56.280 --> 00:12:59.336
report higher levels
of marital satisfaction.

00:12:59.360 --> 00:13:01.376
So when men share housework and childcare,